# Data Property: <http://www.linkedmodel.org/schema/vaem#intent> (intent)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.linkedmodel.org/schema/vaem#intent> "intent")
DataPropertyRange(<http://www.linkedmodel.org/schema/vaem#intent> xsd:string)

# Data Property: <http://www.linkedmodel.org/schema/vaem#latestPublishedVersion> (latest published version)

