SubClassOf(<http://www.linkedmodel.org/schema/vaem#Party> DataMaxCardinality(1 <http://www.linkedmodel.org/schema/vaem#url>))

# Class: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> (Concept)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> "Concept"@en)
